description:
Micah Myers is a freelance comic book letterer from Portsmouth, VA. He lives with his wife, Tiffany, and is training his two children, Jacob and Charis, in the ways of comic book fandom.

Micah has lettered comics for multiple companies such as Zenescope, Alterna Comics, 215 Ink, and Devil's Due. He has lettered several pitch stories for Kelly Bender and Mark Bertolini. He is the letterer for All Hallow's Eve and SNARL.
name: Micah Myers
